OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1783793977
OL,3,CMan charged with murder following
OL,4,Cfatal fire on Isle of Wight
OL,6,FA man has been charged with murder
OL,7,Ffollowing a fatal fire on the Isle of
OL,8,FWight.
OL,10,FPolice were called at 3.32am on Friday
OL,11,F26 June to reports of a fire at an
OL,12,Faddress on Ronsons Close, Cowes.
OL,14,FOfficers went to the scene along with
OL,15,Fcolleagues from Isle of Wight Fire and
OL,16,FRescue Service and Isle of Wight
OL,17,FAmbulance.
OL,19,FLucas Scutt, aged 24 and from Cowes,
OL,20,Fwas pronounced dead at the scene.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/4
