OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1783793977
OL,3,CMan charged with murder following
OL,4,Cfatal fire on Isle of Wight
OL,6,F24-year-old Liam Matthews, of
OL,7,FSpinnaker Road, Cowes, has now been
OL,8,Fcharged with murder, arson with intent
OL,9,Fto endanger life, and failure to
OL,10,Fcomply with a Section 49 notice to
OL,11,Fdisclose the key to protected
OL,12,Finformation.
OL,14,FHe has been remanded in custody to
OL,15,Fappear at Southampton Magistrates'
OL,16,FCourt on Saturday 11 July.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/4
