OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1783793977
OL,3,CMan charged with murder following
OL,4,Cfatal fire on Isle of Wight
OL,6,FA second 24-year-old man from Cowes
OL,7,Farrested on suspicion of murder and
OL,8,Farson with intent to endanger life,
OL,9,Fhas now been released from bail and
OL,10,Fwill face no further action in
OL,11,Frelation to those offences.
OL,13,FPreviously, a 59-year-old man from
OL,14,FCowes arrested on suspicion of murder
OL,15,Fand arson with intent to endanger life
OL,16,Fwas released from bail and will face
OL,17,Fno further action in relation to those
OL,18,Foffences.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/4
