OL,3,CMan charged with murder following
OL,4,Cfatal fire on Isle of Wight
OL,6,FA 28-year-old man from Ventnor, who
OL,7,Fwas arrested on suspicion of murder,
OL,8,Farson with intent to endanger life,
OL,9,Fand possession of an offensive weapon
OL,10,Fin a public place was previously
OL,11,Fbailed with conditions until Sunday 27
OL,12,FSeptember to allow for further
OL,13,Fenquiries to be carried out.
